item.description:
&quot;Thames Water has cut off the natural spring water inflow to Nixon&#39;s Lake (the duck pond), replacing it with an inappropriate surface processing unit. The pond is now stagnant, creating a foul odour and a severe breeding ground for mosquitoes. We demand the council press Thames Water to restore the natural spring water inflow immediately.&quot;
